{"tid":667100,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美股前瞻|業績超預期，騰訊ADR盤前大漲逾5％","createTime":"2018-05-16T12:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T13:00:29.000Z","uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"981fbfab306ad8bcffb736ea61d920ae616eb686","tid":667100,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T12:45:58.000Z","msg":"牛牛圈啲新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1897702a5772a22a6bd9e09e7b02833e9679c3","tid":667100,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T12:46:50.000Z","msg":"腾讯第一季度净利润232.9亿元人民币，市场预期174.2亿元人民币；营收735.3亿元人民币，市场预期707.8亿元人民币。腾讯一季度网络游戏收入同比增长26%至人民币287.78亿元，环比也实现14.4%的增幅，利润与营收打破市场预期。<br />\n<br />\n【热点要闻】<br />\n<br />\n中国3月增持美债110亿美元 总规模创五个月新高<br />\n<br />\n北京时间16日早间消息 中国3月份持有的美国国债规模攀升至五个月最高位，中国仍然是美国最大的外国债权人。美国财政部周二公布的国际资本流动报告（TIC）显示，中国持有的美国政府债券、票据和国库券今年3月份增加了110亿美元，总规模达到1.19万亿美元，创五个月新高。"},{"pid":"37d98b2f5382f7410ebae88b165f5ffcf8f79755","tid":667100,"uid":81150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"981fbfab306ad8bcffb736ea61d920ae616eb686","tid":667100,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T12:45:58.000Z","msg":"牛牛圈啲新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T12:47:09.000Z","msg":"大  <span style=\"font-size: large;\">牛</span>  <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三</span> !!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3abdda386ccf5265fc3b3ae951f6578660ac8133","tid":667100,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37d98b2f5382f7410ebae88b165